---
title: Seared Double Steak & Mustardy Greens with Garlic-Peppercorn Butter & Mash
description: Long after you finish this humble dinner of steak and greens, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple
addition of tangy wholegrain mustard cooked into the veggies. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease of life.

*Keep an eye out...
Due to recent sourcing
challenges, we’ve replaced
leek with courgette, which may
be a little different to what’s
pictured. Don’t worry, your
recipe will be just
as delicious!*
